==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Glaciation
<hw>Gla`ci*a"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Act
of freezing.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>That which is formed by freezing; ice.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>The process of glaciating, or the state of being
glaciated; the production of glacial phenomena.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Glacier</ent>⟦br⟧
